HEADWORD: Loanable
<hw>Loan"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Such as can be
lent; available for lending; <as>as, <ex>loanable</ex> funds</as>; --
used mostly in financial business and writings.</def>⟦br⟧
